WEBVTT

00:00.312 --> 00:02.158
Whoo!

00:02.159 --> 00:03.874
Enjoying your flight today, Emma?

00:03.875 --> 00:06.547
Just warn me if we're
heading for Aca-puko, okay?

00:07.689 --> 00:10.631
- Knock-knock! Danny?
- Riley, hi.

00:10.632 --> 00:12.469
Ben, don't bother. I'm not talking to you.

00:12.470 --> 00:15.018
But if I were I'd be saying, "I
can't believe you slept with Heather."

00:15.019 --> 00:16.795
- Listen, listen, I'm so sorry.
- Really, I don't need to...

00:16.796 --> 00:18.198
- just hear me out.
- I don't wanna hear the whole thing!

00:18.199 --> 00:19.579
- It's really not necessary!
- Just shut up already!

00:20.886 --> 00:22.438
I'm trying to apologize here.

00:23.076 --> 00:25.476
Listen, I am so sorry I slept with Heather.

00:25.477 --> 00:26.624
If I knew you hated her,

00:26.625 --> 00:27.926
I would've done the right thing...

00:28.228 --> 00:29.899
I would've snuck her out the fire escape.

00:32.301 --> 00:34.023
- Is your brother here or not?
- Not.

00:34.024 --> 00:35.466
- Okay.
- No no, Riley, wait wait wait.

00:35.467 --> 00:36.974
Please please please. I promise you

00:36.975 --> 00:39.201
I will never ever hook
up with Heather again.

00:39.623 --> 00:41.444
Well, you couldn't even if you wanted to,

00:41.445 --> 00:43.472
so not really that big of a sacrifice.

00:44.814 --> 00:47.326
Oh...  I could.

00:48.238 --> 00:50.816
She was into me, but I'm choosing not to,

00:50.817 --> 00:52.408
because I'm just that kinda guy.

00:53.951 --> 00:55.837
Oh. Well, sorry to burst your man-bubble,

00:55.838 --> 00:58.224
but Heather only used
you to get even with me.

00:58.225 --> 01:00.653
And it just helped that you
have no morals or integrity.

01:01.677 --> 01:03.276
- Oh? Really? Oh, okay.
- Yeah.

01:03.277 --> 01:07.184
Would a woman... Who
never wants to see me again

01:07.185 --> 01:08.844
leave an earring?

01:10.012 --> 01:11.608
She's practically moving in!

01:12.831 --> 01:15.899
Oh. Okay. Whatever you say, yeah.

01:15.900 --> 01:18.354
Well, I say I could go out with
her again any time I wanted to.

01:18.355 --> 01:20.452
Well, I say I challenge you.

01:20.453 --> 01:21.839
Oh, really? Are we gonna go there?

01:21.840 --> 01:23.267
Oh, I think we're already there.

01:23.268 --> 01:25.532
Fine. I bet I can go on a date with Heather

01:25.533 --> 01:28.643
- in the next 48 hours.
-  And I accept that bet.

01:28.644 --> 01:32.780
- Should we wager the usual?
- How about the usual deluxe?

01:33.479 --> 01:35.272
Ho ho.

01:37.743 --> 01:39.580
Oh man.

01:39.947 --> 01:41.471
Oh, this is gonna be good.

01:41.472 --> 01:43.198
Okay.

01:44.410 --> 01:46.497
Hey, what's up, Heather? It's Ben.

01:47.634 --> 01:48.976
Wheeler.

01:51.550 --> 01:53.120
We had sex.

01:54.601 --> 01:56.338
Heather? Heather!

01:58.658 --> 02:00.103
She's gonna call me back.

02:03.095 --> 02:12.973
