see that new disaster movie

06:04.794 --> 06:07.372
but why buy the ticket when
they're showing one for free here?

06:07.373 --> 06:09.910
Yeah, plus we got great seats.

06:10.359 --> 06:11.976
Don't forget to turn off your cellphone.

06:11.977 --> 06:14.609
