Heather, hi. You look lovely as always.

06:17.889 --> 06:20.541
You met me once. Can I have my earring?

06:20.851 --> 06:22.561
Not till you've met Emma.

06:23.388 --> 06:24.699
Hi, Heather.

06:24.700 --> 06:26.775
How'd you like to go
out with my daddy again?

06:26.776 --> 06:28.373
He sure does like you.

06:28.374 --> 06:29.936
Oh, sweetie, they all do.

06:30.740 --> 06:32.003
Now can I have my earring?

06:32.004 --> 06:34.098
Here here, just hold her 10 seconds

06:34.099 --> 06:35.378
and I'll give you back the earring.

06:35.832 --> 06:38.522
Come on. Come on.

06:39.704 --> 06:41.323
There you go.

06:41.783 --> 06:45.531
- Yeah.
- Aww. She is awfully cute.

06:50.771 --> 06:53.600
Here. Your baby's broken.

06:54.269 --> 06:57.967
Sorry. If you let it dry,
you can chip it off later.

06:57.968 --> 06:59.267
Earring!

07:00.862 --> 07:02.372
Gimme that.

07:03.992 --> 07:07.115
- Bravo.
- Wow. Well done.

07:07.116 --> 07:08.787
We loved every minute of that,

07:08.788 --> 07:10.790
- even though the ending was kinda predictable.
- Yeah.

07:11.685 --> 07:15.404
Hey, maybe next time you'll think
twice about baby-blocking me.

07:16.549 --> 07:18.520
Wow. I had no idea

07:18.521 --> 07:20.435
you'd be going down so quickly.

07:20.436 --> 07:22.484
I gotta start working on your punishment.

07:23.008 --> 07:25.371
Do you know where I
can find a video camera,

07:25.372 --> 07:27.711
some hair-removal cream and a tarp?

07:32.207 --> 07:35.370
This is a disaster! I
mean, what do I do now?

07:35.737 --> 07:37.566
You gotta smooth it out first.

07:39.175 --> 07:41.257
Not the dollar! Brad!

07:41.935 --> 07:43.234
Well, there's nothing to do.

07:43.235 --> 07:45.026
Now that you love him,
everything's perfect.

07:45.027 --> 07:47.553
Well, Danny... Danny, I don't love him.

07:47.554 --> 07:49.772
I just got caught up in the moment.

07:49.773 --> 07:52.519
Listen, just go down to
that fountain in the lobby

07:52.520 --> 07:54.267
and fish me out some quarters.

07:54.268 --> 07:55.523
But those are other people's wishes.

07:55.524 --> 07:57.000
Just go!

08:04.429 --> 08:05.847
You know, if you pound
it left of the spring,

08:05.848 --> 08:07.370
it'll give you what you want.

08:09.206 --> 08:11.584
Funny, I come with the same instructions.

08:12.574 --> 08:14.852
I'm not sure you should buy
anything from that machine.

08:14.853 --> 08:16.530
Some of those chips are as old as me.

08:16.531 --> 08:18.887
Well, I prefer the phrase
"aged to perfection."

08:19.902 --> 08:21.438
In that case, I'm Jim.

08:21.439 --> 08:22.778
Hi, Jim, I'm Bonnie.

08:23.197 --> 08:25.469
I hope I'm not being too
forward, but are you single?

08:26.461 --> 08:28.225
Heading in that direction.

08:29.530 --> 08:31.988
Then you'd consider having drinks with me?

08:31.989 --> 08:34.339
Well, consider it considered.

08:35.624 --> 08:37.203
- Can I get your number?
- Sure.

08:37.688 --> 08:40.900
