breaking up with Brad.

10:31.933 --> 10:34.803
I mean, he's smart, he's
funny, he's generous.

10:34.804 --> 10:37.596
Ooh, that's good. Tell him all
that stuff when you dump him.

10:40.961 --> 10:42.798
- Brad, hey.
- Hey.

10:42.799 --> 10:44.153
Great to see you up and about,

10:44.154 --> 10:45.659
looking like you're ready for anything.

10:46.603 --> 10:48.184
Absolutely anything.

10:49.032 --> 10:51.015
I'm actually really
glad that you stopped by.

10:51.016 --> 10:54.542
Hey, what do you think
about me asking your mom

10:54.543 --> 10:56.400
to move in with me?

10:56.953 --> 11:00.215
Umm, I think you should ask
me again in about two minutes.

11:01.308 --> 11:02.915
So, Brad...

11:02.916 --> 11:05.811
She just makes me feel
like no one ever has before.

11:05.812 --> 11:08.434
You know, I wanna take care
of her, I wanna make her happy.

11:08.435 --> 11:09.791
We belong together, you know?

11:10.193 --> 11:13.563
She's just... she's just perfect for me.

11:14.769 --> 11:15.982
You know what?

11:15.983 --> 11:17.638
My mom is perfect for you.

11:18.882 --> 11:20.150
That's what I've been saying!

11:20.545 --> 11:23.242
In fact, I literally just said that.

11:23.803 --> 11:25.372
You definitely shouldn't break up.

11:25.373 --> 11:28.231
- Why would we break up?
- Um, exactly!

11:28.232 --> 11:29.758
So let's go find her,

11:29.759 --> 11:31.795
